      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/lvmh-posts-subdued-sales-as-wealthy-shoppers-remain-cautious</link>
      <description><![CDATA[LVMH 时装和皮革制品销售额在第四季度出现下滑，令奢侈品需求快速复苏的前景蒙上阴影。]]></description>
